Africa's Next Top Model - Season 1, Episode 2




Before the girls got too comfortable in the model house, it was time for their first challenge: a video shoot for the opening sequence for Africa's Next Top Model. But first, they needed to be transformed by international styling guru Carl Isaacs. As the hair fell, so did the tears, with a few girls not quite loving their new looks.




Original Air Date: 17-Nov-2013
